title: UNLV's Yunker, once a part of UNR program, helps Rebels win back Fremont Cannon
text:
Published By: Las Vegas Sun - Today 
He once celebrated when the UNLV football team lost to rival UNR. He was there when the blue Fremont Cannon was wheeled into the locker room...
